</emphasis>
Head; 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[708,751,1909,1931]" pageId="10" pageNumber="193">(10)</emphasis>
Pronotum and mesonotum; 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1045,1086,1909,1931]" pageId="10" pageNumber="193">(11)</emphasis>
Antennal segments III–VIII; 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1394,1436,1909,1931]" pageId="10" pageNumber="193">(12)</emphasis>
Male sternite VIII; 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[347,389,1940,1962]" pageId="10" pageNumber="193">(13)</emphasis>
